title: BS5 AUS based discord 300+ users.
body:
Hi All,

BS5 is an Australian based Discord server, We currently have 300+ users but am always looking for fresh faces.

With a healthy mix of players from bronze to challenger.

We run 3-5 in-house tournaments weekly, Including a current Battle of the Nations comp. with prizes at allot of them.

We also have a active flex que you can join if you want to level up as a part of a 5 man comp.

We are a friendly bunch so pop in and say hello.

https://discord.gg/bvxPHRX

Cheers
Vicelore
